snippet.title: Pikmin 4 : Infinity Cave - Mod Overview Trailer
snippet.description:
In order for this mod to be completed we currently need people with experience in Unreal Engine 4 Modding + Blueprints + IO Store + Depedency/Manifest Knowledge.

If you would like to assist in the development of this project, please reach out to me on Discord.

Discord User: "portable_productions" or portable_productions

If my DM's are off, please send me a friend request, thank you!

If you can't get a hold of me for any reason, please visit the Discord below.

► Visit My Discord - https://discord.gg/7ZUZjTSK7v
